				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\frac{n(n-1)}{2}$$\end{document}n(n−1)2 unique coefficients (from either the upper or lower triangle of the matrix). The following defines and characterizes each identified measure quantifying FC, a summary of which is presented in Supplementary Table 2.

